ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR MANGADEX API USAGE

This software uses the MangaDex API and must comply with MangaDex's terms of service:

1. Attribution Requirements:
   - MUST credit MangaDex (https://mangadex.org)
   - MUST credit scanlation groups for their work
   - MUST NOT remove or obscure credits

2. Usage Restrictions:
   - CANNOT run advertisements alongside MangaDex content
   - CANNOT operate paid services using MangaDex content
   - CANNOT use for commercial purposes without permission
   - MUST respect rate limits (~5 requests/second)

3. Content Guidelines:
   - MUST respect content ratings and age restrictions
   - MUST NOT redistribute content in violation of copyright
   - MUST NOT use for piracy or illegal distribution

4. API Compliance:
   - MUST follow MangaDex API documentation
   - MUST implement proper rate limiting
   - MUST handle errors appropriately
   - MUST NOT attempt to circumvent API restrictions

For full MangaDex terms of service, visit: https://mangadex.org/terms

DISCLAIMER: This software is provided for educational and personal use only.
Users are responsible for ensuring their use complies with all applicable laws
and terms of service.
